snippet.title: My Name In Lights - Roommates official trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.winterwolves.com/roommates.htm
This is the Roommates official trailer. Roomates is a dating sim where you can play as Max or Anne, and romance your roommates, including same-sex romance.

The game is available for Windows, Mac, Linux, Android and iOS. Check the first link for more info!
